               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I was standing by the house, out of the rain, and a man came up, and seeing I was cold and hungry, he took me in and treated me; he gave me the shilling to pay for the bread and cheese; he was a stranger to me.</p>
